data.description: Welcome to this beautiful single story, updated home.  Featuring an open floor plan, updated kitchen with soft close cabinets, granite counter tops, and stainless steel appliances. This home also has a newer roof and A/C unit, fresh paint, new front door, full spacious basement, large 2 car attached garage that is accessible from the main floor, basement and backyard.  Large fenced in backyard with patio, garden, firepit and storage shed and so much more! Plus, you will never get left in the dark with this home's whole house natural gas-powered generator. Conveniently located just a short drive to Columbus, Circleville, or Lancaster!  This home is turn key and ready to be yours!
